0190Web Interface Plug-In
0200---------------------
0210The Web Interface Plug-In provides the following functions:
0220 - Program generation such as HTML to Natural conversion.
0230 - Class generation.
0240 - Online test utility to check subprograms locally without involving
0250   an HTTP server.
0260 - Set Natural Web options.
