0290Basic Modules
0300-------------
0310The basic module names of the Natural Web Interface are prefixed
0320with W3.
0330
0340They provide the communication between Natural subprograms and the HTTP
0350Server Extension. All other programs of the Natural Web Interface use
0360these programs.
0370
0380It is possible to make some administrative changes to define the amount
0390and format of the transferred data, to change conversion tables and to
0400change the error page.
0410
