0430Online Documentation
0440--------------------
0450The online documentation files are prefixed with E3 and T3.
0460The online documentation contains example programs that can be
0470displayed and executed online. Depending on your installation of the
0480Natural Web Interface, call the subprogram NAT-DOCU from the library
0490SYSWEB3 to display the main page of online documentation at your web
0500browser.
0510
0520Example of the URL to call the online documentation:
0530  http://yourserver/yourcgi3/sysweb3/nat-docu
0540
0550Note:
0560To display the online documentation, the HTTP Server Extensions of the
0570Natural Web Interface must be installed and a correct Natural RPC/DCOM
0580Server has to be started. To access the program USR1057N, of library
0590SYSEXT, add a steplib to SYSEXT or copy the programs to your system
0600library.
