0630Demo Application
0640----------------
0650The demonstration application delivered shows simple file maintenance
0660with select functions. The demonstration is based on the Adabas file
0670EMPLOYEES. To run the application, Adabas has to be active.
0680
0690The implementation of the demonstration application uses templates, XML
0700and XSLT, name prefix D6* Depending on your installation of the HTTP
0710Server Extensions, call the subprogram D6INDEX from the library
0720SYSWEB3.
0730
0740Example of the URL to call the demonstration application:
0750  http://yourserver/yourcgi/sysweb3/d6index
0760
