0780Pictures
0790--------
0800All pictures needed are delivered with the Natural Web Interface
0810in the Natural installation folder, for example in
0820  ...\Natural\INSTALL\nww3\http-root\pictures
0830
0840Save them at your HTTP server at the remote directory /pictures.
0850If you want to use another remote directory name, set the environment
0860variable PICTURES at the initialization file of your HTTP Server
0870Extension with the specific remote directory name.
0880
0890
0900Javascript
0910----------
0920All JavaScript needed are delivered with the Natural Web Interface.
0930Save the directory javascript at your HTTP server at the remote
0940directory /javascript. If you want to use another remote directory
0950name, set the environment variable JAVASCRIPT at the initialization
0960file of your Natural Web Server Extension with the specific remote
0970directory name.
